flowchart TD
    Start([Start])
    Start --> A{Is ROIC > Cost of Capital by ≥ 2%?}
    A -- Yes --> B{Is ROE ≥ 15%\nand stable/growing?}
    A -- No --> Reject1[Reject Company]

    B -- Yes --> C{Is Debt to Equity Ratio < 1.0?}
    B -- No --> Reject2[Reject Company]

    C -- Yes --> D{Is OCF positive\nand growing?}
    C -- No --> Reject3[Reject Company]

    D -- Yes --> E{Is FCF positive\nand consistent?}
    D -- No --> Reject4[Reject or Further Analysis]

    E -- Yes --> F{Is Reinvestment Rate appropriate\nfor growth stage?}
    E -- No --> Reject5[Reject or Investigate]

    F -- Yes --> G{Does Intrinsic Value > Market Price\n(DCF Analysis)?}
    F -- No --> Reject6[Reject or Additional Analysis]

    G -- Yes --> H{Is Dividend Discount Model favorable?}
    G -- No --> Reject7[Reject or Reassess Assumptions]

    H -- Yes --> I{Is P/E Ratio lower\nthan industry peers?}
    H -- No --> Reject8[Reject or Reassess]

    I -- Yes --> J{Is Free-Float high\n(indicating good liquidity)?}
    I -- No --> K[Consider Implications]

    J -- Yes --> L{Is Dividend Yield above\nindustry average?}
    J -- No --> M[Caution: Potential Liquidity Issues]

    L -- Yes --> N{Is Dividend Payout Ratio < 60%?}
    L -- No --> O[Consider Overall Return]

    N -- Yes --> P{Meets all critical metrics?}
    N -- No --> Q[Caution: Dividend Sustainability]

    P -- Yes --> Invest[[**Invest**]]
    P -- Mostly Yes --> Hold[[**Hold**\nFurther Analysis]]
    P -- No --> Avoid[[**Avoid**]]

    K --> J
    M --> L
    O --> N
    Q --> P

    Reject1 & Reject2 & Reject3 & Reject4 & Reject5 & Reject6 & Reject7 & Reject8 --> End([End])
    Avoid --> End
    Invest --> End
    Hold --> End
